snippet.title: Johnny Depp wanted ex-wife Amber Heard to 'cut him'
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp's libel hearing has been played an audio recording of the star asking his ex-wife to cut him with a knife.

The three-and-a-half-minute recording, believed to be from July 2016, was played on the fourth day of the star's libel case against the publisher of The Sun newspaper.

The Hollywood star is suing the The Sun newspaper over claims he was violent towards Heard.
